                            <para>Pulse Rate 68 bpm, taken by pulse oximeter</para>
                            <editorial-rule>
                                <title>Topic with a Result Value</title>
                                <mathphrase>Any Topic that states a Result that has a value will be
                                    specified with the correct upperBound, lowerBound, and
                                    measureSemantic.</mathphrase> If the Result is a single value,
                                the upperBound and lowerBound will be the same value.  If the Result
                                is a range, the upperBound and lowerBound will be specifed as
